🔹 Fetch Types
Type
Meaning
EAGER (default)
Loads immediately
LAZY
Loads only when needed

@OneToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)

⚠️ Important
Lazy loading in OneToOne may need proxy handling.

🔹 Cascade Types
@OneToOne(cascade = CascadeType.ALL)

Cascade
Meaning
PERSIST
Save child automatically
MERGE
